result.name: Yoshinoya

reviews.text:
This Yoshinoya located on the level three of Shun Tak Centre, right opposite to the departure gate to ferry, good place for a quick bite before you take the ferry.
No comment on the food of chain restaurant.  The hygiene of the restaurant just OK, the floor is not well cleaned.  And here usually full of people during the lunch peak time.  And they prepare the food well fast, usually take you less than 5mins.  But there is no toilet around the restaurant
Poor attitude. Forced me to pay in Octopus cause she saw me carrying one in my wallet. The 2 star is for the food.
Japanese fast food , not much choice, a quick bite is ok.
it is very yummy,why yooshin yang said it is not yummy?
The employee receiving orders couldn't speak English. Both beef bowl and chicken bowl were absolutely the worst I've had in Yoshinoya from multiple countries.

reviews.text: 在林士街政府合署完成學生檢查,正好是下午茶時段 。與囝囝跑到旁邊的信德中心,享用價廉物美的吉野家牛肉飯,真的太幸福了！
